&lt;p&gt;To protect yourself from recruitment scams, please note that Nex communicates through official company emails ending in @nex.inc. If you receive a suspicious email or message, please do not respond and report it immediately to us.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: Hong Kong&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Type: Full Time&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
