&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-block-4&quot; style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Produce high-quality 3D game art, characters, environments, and supporting assets, ensuring they are perfectly integrated for in-game use and under the desired art direction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-block-4&quot; style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Develop and implement particle systems, animations, and other dynamic visual elements directly within Unity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-block-4&quot; style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Create custom shaders and stunning visual effects using Unity Shader Graph to give our games their unique, vibrant look.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-block-4&quot; style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Rigorously optimize 3D game assets, textures, and visual elements to ensure smooth,

