&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sports game title for &lt;strong&gt;Nex Playground&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Anime-inspired sports game visual style&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with, or a strong interest in, sports games is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
