&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience working with &lt;strong&gt;Unity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to create high-quality environment assets while meeting &lt;strong&gt;mobile-level performance budgets&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with mobile platform optimization, efficient asset creation, and performance-conscious workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience optimizing environments for lower-spec hardware is highly desirable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of anime-inspired or stylized art direction, including shape language, color, lighting, and composition&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to translate anime aesthetics into compelling environment design through modeling, texturing, lighting, and overall scene presentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Nice to Have&lt;/h3&gt;

