&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Engineering, Publishing, and other teams on the production and promotion of our games.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help cultivate a strong Design team culture and share creative leadership responsibilities through feedback and coaching efforts, in coordination with the Senior Director of Design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
