&lt;p&gt;To protect yourself from recruitment scams, please note that Nex communicates through official company emails ending in @nex.inc. If you receive a suspicious email or message, please do not respond and report it immediately to us.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;paragraph-3&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: Remote (USA &amp;amp;&amp;nbsp;Canada only)&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Annual salary: USD 120,000 - USD150,000&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Type: Full-Time&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reports to: Engineering Manager&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
