&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a QA Engineer who loves games, sweats the details, and enjoys learning new technology. Motion-based QA is different from traditional game QA: you’ll test with your whole body in real-world environments (lighting, room sizes, player heights, 1–4 players, etc.). Prior motion-gaming experience is &lt;em&gt;not required&lt;/em&gt;—strong QA fundamentals and a learning mindset are.&lt;/p&gt;
