&lt;li&gt;Test motion-game fundamentals such as responsiveness/latency, recognition consistency, occlusion handling, and edge cases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform functional, usability, regression, localization, and device/compatibility testing across the product surface area.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write excellent bug reports with clear repro steps, expected vs. actual results, environment details, and short video captures when helpful.&lt;/li&gt;
